%h2=@page_title

%p
  To bulk add a user to affiliates using a CSV file, follow these instructions:
  %ul.bulk-upload-instructions
    %li Create a plain text file with a .csv extension.
    %li List one affiliate name per row in the first column. Headers are optional and will be ignored.
    %li Example format:
    %li
      %textarea{ rows: 2, readonly: true }
        Example Affiliate 1
        Example Affiliate 2
    %li Save the file on your computer.
    %li Browse for the file using the field below.
    %li Enter the userâ€™s email address.
    %li Click "Upload and Queue Additions".
    %li You will receive an email confirmation once the process is complete.

= form_with url: upload_admin_bulk_affiliate_add_index_path, local: true, multipart: true, class: 'form' do |f|
  .form-group
    = f.label :email, "User Email (Required):", class: 'usa-label'
    = f.text_field :email, required: true, class: 'usa-input'
  .form-group
    = f.label :file, "Select CSV file of Affiliate Names:", class: 'usa-label'
    = f.file_field :file, required: true, accept: '.csv', class: 'usa-file-input'
  %p
  = f.submit "Upload and Queue Additions", class: 'usa-button usa-button--secondary'